column2: SELECT TOP #  p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z,  p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field,  s.specobjid, s.specClass, s.z,  s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid FROM Galaxy AS G JOIN ZooNoSpec as zns ON g.objid = zns.objid WHERE   p.u BETWEEN # AND #  AND g BETWEEN # AND #
